OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784067502
OL,3,CMan, 21, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Caffray after reports of threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FA 21-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of affray following reports
OL,9,Fof threatening behaviour in Newport.
OL,11,FOfficers from Gwent Police, including
OL,12,Ffirearms officers, were called to an
OL,13,Faddress in St Edward Street shortly
OL,14,Fbefore midnight on Friday (10 July).
OL,16,FUpon arrival, a man was found in
OL,17,Fpossession of a crossbow, and was shot
OL,18,Fby officers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
