PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784067502
OL,3,CMan, 21, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Caffray after reports of threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FHe received first aid at the scene and
OL,8,Fwas taken to hospital, where he
OL,9,Fremains in a stable condition.
OL,11,FThe man has also been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of threats to kill and
OL,13,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,15,FHe is currently in police custody at
OL,16,Fhospital as enquiries continue.
OL,18,FIn a statement, Gwent Police's Deputy
OL,19,FChief Constable, Nicholas McLain, said:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784067502
OL,3,CMan, 21, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Caffray after reports of threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,F"We understand this matter may cause
OL,8,Fconcern, but I want to reassure the
OL,9,Fpublic that it was isolated and there
OL,10,Fis no wider or ongoing risk; we are
OL,11,Fnot looking for anyone else in
OL,12,Fconnection with this matter.
OL,14,F"Reports involving firearms and
OL,15,Fweapons are rare in Gwent, but we take
OL,16,Fthem extremely seriously and respond
OL,17,Fprofessionally and proportionately to
OL,18,Fthe risk presented.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
