PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784067502
OL,3,CMan, 21, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Caffray after reports of threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,F"Our firearms officers are highly
OL,8,Ftrained and held to the highest
OL,9,Fstandards. The discharge of a police
OL,10,Ffirearm is always a last resort and
OL,11,Fonly occurs where there is a
OL,12,Fsignificant threat to officers, the
OL,13,Findividual involved, or members of the
OL,14,Fpublic.
OL,16,F"They do an incredibly difficult job,
OL,17,Foften making split-second decisions in
OL,18,Fhigh-pressure situations, and I
OL,19,Fcommend those who voluntarily take on
OL,20,Fthat responsibility."
